<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/login.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-Vkoo8x4CGsO3+Hhxv8T/Q5PaXtkKtu6ug5TOeNV6gBiFeWPGFN9MuhOf23Q9Ifjh" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/ionicons/2.0.1/css/ionicons.min.css" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/axios/dist/axios.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://www.google.com/recaptcha/api.js" async defer></script>
    <title>Voting</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="login-dark" style="height: 100vh;">
        <div>
            <h2 class="sr-only">Login Form</h2>
            <div class="illustration">
                <p style="font-size:20%;">
                    <a href='https://github.com/NTHU-SA/Voting-DSA'>-使用清大學生會開源選舉系統-</a>
                </p>
                <p style="font-size:10%;">
                    "此平台使用爬蟲登入高科大校務行政資訊系統請放心，投票系統不會紀錄您的密碼"
                </p>
                <i class="icon ion-ios-locked-outline"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input id="account-input" class="form-control" type="text" name="email" placeholder="校務系統學號" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <input id="password-input" class="form-control" type="password" name="password" placeholder="校務系統密碼" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <div
                    class="g-recaptcha"
                    data-sitekey={{RECAPTCHA}}
                    data-theme="dark" data-size="normal">
                </div>
              </div>
            <div id="form-prompt" style="text-align: center;">
                <p>* 資訊輸入錯誤，請再試一次</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <!--img src="/auth/ccxp/captcha" alt="" /-->
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <button class="btn btn-primary btn-block" onclick="signIn($('#account-input')[0].value, $('#password-input')[0].value, $('#g-recaptcha-response')[0].value)">
            Log In
          </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="./js/utils.js"></script>
    <script src="./js/signIn.js"></script>
    <script>
        // console.log(jwtToken);
        if (jwtToken === "" || jwtToken === undefined) {
            // alert("此平台使用清大計中 OAuth 2 登入驗證，將協助您重新導向\n請放心，投票系統不會取得您的帳密");
            // window.location =
            //     "/auth_url";
        } else {
            window.location = "voting.html";
        }
    </script>
</body>

</html>
